# DA-3: Conditional Logic Placement
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any branching logic introduction

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Low-Level Class: Class handling concrete implementation.
- Factory/Strategy Pattern: Design patterns used to encapsulate conditional logic.

ENFORCE: Conditional logic must reside in low-level classes or factory/strategy patterns.
PROHIBIT: High-level if/else branching in top-level modules; conditionals that violate SRP.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Design Coherence Enforcer Skill; suggest refactor.
